Jose Mourinho could one day make a shock return to manage Real Madrid , according to Real defender Alvaro Arbeloa .
The Chelsea manager ended his three-year spell in Madrid to rejoin his current club in 2013 , leaving the Spanish capital amid rumours of bust-ups with senior players , club captain Iker Casillas , Sergio Ramos and Pepe .
But right back Arbelo says Real 's door is a possibility of Jose Mourinho could return to Real Madrid one day .
Mourinho left Madrid and rejoined Chelsea in 2013 .